tiles.title: Search by text
tiles.description: Enter a search value in the parameters to explore errors

queries.text:
pageViews
| extend cd = parse_json(customDimensions)
| extend env = tostring(cd.environmentId)
| where env == _environment
| where timestamp > _startTime
| where timestamp < _endTime
| summarize durationSeconds = round(avg(duration) / 1000, 0), count() by name
| order by durationSeconds desc

exceptions
| extend cd = parse_json(customDimensions)
| extend env = tostring(cd.environmentId)
| where env == _environment
| where timestamp > _startTime
| where timestamp < _endTime
| project timestamp, env, outerMessage, outerType
| summarize count() by outerMessage, outerType
| order by count_ desc

exceptions
| extend cd = parse_json(customDimensions)
| extend env = tostring(cd.environmentId)
| where env == _environment
| where timestamp > _startTime
| where timestamp < _endTime
| extend CallStack = tostring(cd.CallStack)
| extend ClassName = tostring(cd.ClassName)
| extend activityId = tostring(cd.activityId)
| extend BatchJobId = tolong(cd.BatchJobId)
| project timestamp,outerMessage, outerType, CallStack, ClassName,activityId, BatchJobId
| where _searchText != "" and  (CallStack contains _searchText or outerMessage contains _searchText or ClassName contains _searchText)

pageViews
| extend cd = parse_json(customDimensions)
| extend env = tostring(cd.environmentId)
| where env == _environment
| where timestamp > _startTime
| where timestamp < _endTime
| where name contains _formName
| extend durationSeconds = round(duration / 1000, 0)
| project timestamp, name, durationSeconds, user_Id, cd.activityId //, cd
| order by durationSeconds desc

customEvents
| where name in ("BatchStatusUpdate")
| extend cd = parse_json(customDimensions)
| extend env = tostring(cd.environmentId)
| extend SessionId = tostring(cd.SessionId)
| extend Orders = tostring(cd.Orders)
| extend BatchJobId = tolong(cd.BatchJobId)
| extend BatchJobTaskId = tolong(cd.BatchJobTaskId)
| extend ChildBatchJobId = tolong(cd.ChildBatchJobId)
| extend ElapsedMilliseconds = tolong(cd.ElapsedMilliseconds)
| extend Company = toupper(cd.DataAreaId)
| extend User = cd.CurrentUserId
| where env == _environment
| where timestamp > _startTime
| where timestamp < _endTime
| extend currentStatus = tostring(cd.NewStatus)
| extend prevStatus = tostring(cd.OrigStatus)
| extend Caption = tostring(cd.BatchJobName)
| extend Error = tostring(cd.Error)
| extend ExecutingBy = tostring(cd.ExecutingBy)
| extend Reccurence = tostring(cd.Reccurence)
| extend CreatedBy = tostring(cd.CreatedBy)
| extend StartDateTime = todatetime(cd.StartDateTime)
| extend EndDateTime = todatetime(cd.EndDateTime)
| extend AOS = tostring(cd.AOS)
| project  timestamp, SessionId, name, Company, ElapsedMilliseconds, User, BatchJobId, BatchJobTaskId, Caption, currentStatus, prevStatus, StartDateTime, cd, AOS
| summarize max(timestamp), arg_max(timestamp, Caption), arg_max(timestamp, currentStatus), arg_max(timestamp, StartDateTime) , arg_max(timestamp, cd) by BatchJobId, BatchJobTaskId, AOS
| where currentStatus == "Executing"
| project BatchJobId, BatchJobTaskId, Status = currentStatus, Caption, lastUpdate = max_timestamp, AOS
